Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,1881年  罗马尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.78,0:00:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,本字幕纯属学习交流\N===原创翻译  转载标明===
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,招贤纳士：QQ群233183580\N===如有翻译疏忽  还请指正原谅===
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.78,0:01:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,————祝大家观影愉快————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,历久数载…\NAfter all these long years...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你将变得多么饥饿\Nhow famished you must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  Jezebel啊\NOh, sweet Jezebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快瞧！\NLook!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发了！\NWe're rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,血  就是生命\NThe blood is the life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,宾客均至\NAll the guests have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,（1896年  伦敦）\N入境时需拍照？\NPhotographed upon entry?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,（1896年  伦敦）\N例行安排而已\NAs arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝本如此？\NAnd the prototype?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好按规划演示了吗？\NReady for the demonstration as scheduled?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  先生\NIt is, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,依安排行事\NAs scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,从今天开始\NFrom this day forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你是一个美国实业家\Nyou are an American industrialist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,以美国之神  枪\NAs American as God, guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,以及波旁威士忌的身份…\Nand bourbon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那就依预计行事  - 很好  先生\N- As scheduled. - Very good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好啊\NGood evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Alexander Grayson\NI'm Alexander Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真是激动人心\NIt's breathtaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哇噢  难道不令人兴奋吗？\NWell, isn't this exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我开始喜欢上这个Grayson了  - 谢谢\N- I'm liking this Grayson already. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这杯子的价值比我一周赚得都多\NThis glass is worth more than I earn in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,别显得那么土气  Jonathan\NDon't be gauche, Jonathan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,再说…它比你一个月赚的还多\NBesides...it's worth more than you make in a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy！\NLucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我就开了个玩笑\NI'm only having a bit of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你该不会生我气吧？\NYou're not cross with me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我会受打击的\NI'd be simply devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,当然没有  你是那么迷人\NOf course not. You're far too charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,确实啊  不是吗？\NI am, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了\NI'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那  你会记得你的承诺  对吗？\NNow, you'll remember your promise, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,今夜我是你的客人  不是新闻工作者\NI'm your guest tonight, not a journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他真可爱  对吗？\NHe's such a darling, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Alastair！  你这个坏蛋\NAlastair! You beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你躲哪儿了？\NWhere have you been hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy  亲爱的\NLucy, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真是兼容并收的圈子\NIt's quite an eclectic group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,新高富帅  旧老太爷  还有无产左派\NNew money, old money, no money left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜猜Alexander Grayson是哪个？\NWhich do you suppose is Alexander Grayson?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他肯定会大张旗鼓地介绍自己\NI'm sure he'll announce himself to great fanfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们都是这样做事儿的  - 恩\N- They always do at these things. - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么会让你和我谈论这些…\NHow I ever let you talk me into this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的  有人想窥探你出实验室\NSeriously, somebody had to pry you out of that laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,事实是\NThe truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意和我共度今晚呢\NWho would you rather spend your evening with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说和醉酒蛤蟆呢？\Nor a pickled toad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哈  蛤蟆吧…\NUm, the toad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为  最后还有机会\NBecause at least there's a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,吻的他青蛙变王子\Nmy kiss might turn him into a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哇噢  他很努力吗？\NWell, hasn't he tried hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是用英镑当墙纸贴\NMight as well have papered the walls with pound notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,多么令人不安的美国啊\NHow distressingly American.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,坦白说  我很惊讶这么多人会出席\NFrankly, I'm amazed so many of us turned up at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们目不直视\NHow can we properly mock him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该怎样恰当的嘲笑他们呢？\Nif we haven't set eyes on the man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们  很荣幸向你介绍\NLadies and gentlemen, it is my pleasure to introduce
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,卡菲克斯庄园主  宴会东道主\Nthe master of Carfax Manor, your host,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander Grayson先生\NMister Alexander Grayson!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是他啊  - 是他！\N- It's him. - It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎宾至\NWelcome to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,期望你们来的自由  去的安逸\NMay you come freely, go safely,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,也请你们留下一点快乐和幸福\Nand please, leave some of the happiness you bring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？\NIs everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事  - 你确定？\N- Yes. - Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我就  我刚打了个寒颤\NSomeone walked over my grave, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,恩哼\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女人  蓝绸裙  乳纱缎\NThat woman. Blue satin, creme chiffon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知晓她的一切\NI want to know everything about her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还有和她一起的那个男的  - 好的  先生\N- and the man she's with. - Of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  神秘的Grayson先生\NAh, the mysterious Mister Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是见面了\NFinally we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你是？\NAnd you would be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我本应置身于温暖浴室\NWell, I would be in a nice warm bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但却不得不来\Nbut I simply had to come
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这儿发生了什么破事\Nand find out what all the fuss was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jayne Wetherby  - 恩\N- Jayne Wetherby. - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是Wetherby大人？\NLord Wetherby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  拜托  不是！\NOh, good God, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的  恩  今夜的男伴儿\NThis is my, um, companion for the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我的好朋友  Herr Kruger\Nmy very dear friend, Herr Kruger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为康健干杯\NGesundheit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  我是Clive Dawes\NAh. Sir Clive Dawes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander Grayson\NAlexander Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,请允许我介绍我的夫人  Hope\NPermit me to introduce my wife, Lady Hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是一个难以让人忘怀的舞厅\NWhat an impressive ballroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生\NMister Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还有Davenport大人…\NMay I present Lord Davenport...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurent女士…\NAnd Lady Laurent...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,以及Laurent大人\NAnd Lord Laurent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurent大人\NLord Laurent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了  那  如果我没记错\NSplendid. Now, if I'm not mistaken,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你和Clive先生共同主事\Nyou and sir Clive co-chair
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大英因皮里尔冷剂公司的董事会\Nthe board of British Imperial Coolant Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是董事一员  Grayson先生\NWe sit on a number of boards, Mister Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上你就是\NIndeed you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大英因皮里尔拥有专利\NBritish Imperial holds patents,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,高效冷冻剂的专利\Npatents to high-efficiency coolants
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这对加快我的一个技术项目\Nwhich would be most useful in advancing one of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是非常有用的\Nmy technological projects.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我想拿到这些专利\NI would very much like to acquire those patents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生  大英冷剂公司的任务\NMister Grayson, the British Imperial Company
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是把自己的产品\Nis in the business of selling our products
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,卖给英国企业\Nto British industry,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是把我们潜在的专利\Nnot our underlying patents
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,送来共同殖民地\Nto interloping colonials.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\NDarling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,也许下次\NPerhaps next time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你会让Clive先生\Nyou'll sway sir Clive
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,改变主意\Nthrough his bookmakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知\NHe's an inveterate gambler,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他有赌博的陋习\Nnot a terribly good one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:08:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,而且这可不是个好习惯\Nfrom what I gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonthan！ 你跑去哪里了…\NJonathan! Where did you run...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Alexander Grayson   - Jonathan Harker.\N- Alexander Grayson. - Jonathan Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是我最可爱的朋友\NAnd this is my most lovely friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina Murray小姐\NMiss Mina Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  Mina\NOf course. Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  只是…\NI'm sorry, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我发誓…  - 我们曾经见过？\N- I'd swear... - We've met?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有同感\NI was thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰 先生\NPardon me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 时间到了  - 啊 对\N- It's time. - Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,失陪一下\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我 Renfeild，\NTell me, Renfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan Harker 是谁？\NWho is this Jonathan Harker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,审判者报的记者\NHe's a reporter for the Inquisitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,手上握有很多资源 很精明\NResourceful, tenacious,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而且非常非常有野心\Nand very, very ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  那个女的呢？\NHmm. And the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina Murray  医学生\NMina Murray, medical student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸是William Murray医生\NFather, Doctor William Murray,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bethelem Royal医院的院长\Ndirector of Bethlem Royal Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们 先生们\NLadies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,请集中到舞厅中间来\Nplease, gather in the center of the ballroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker先生  Arem Renfield\NMister Harker. Arem Renfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道请柬上写明了\NYou're aware that the invitation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,拒绝采访吗？\Nexplicitly forbade the press?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以跟你保证\NI can assure you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是来社交的\NI'm purely here on a social basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真遗憾\NWhat a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生会很失望的\NMister Grayson will be disappointed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你一个字都不会写\Nthat you won't be writing at least a word or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你感兴趣  他愿意邀请\NIf you're interested, he would like you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你明天来专访\Nto come by tomorrow for an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一个…一个专访？\NAn... An interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  我很感兴趣\NOf course, I'd be interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  4点半\N430, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  Grayson先生愿意跟大家分享\NAnd now, Mister Grayson would like to share
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:11:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他最近的技术成果的展示！\Na demonstration of his latest technical marvel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的来宾…\NHonored guests...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,当我还是个小男孩的时候\NWhen I was a boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我老爸给我讲了黑暗时代的故事\Nmy father told me stories of the dark ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候只有野蛮的战争和部族\Na time when culture
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,文化和学习在那个年代\Nand learning were eclipsed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,黯然失色\Nby barbaric ritual and war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,经过这些年\NOver the years,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经渐渐相信\NI have come to believe that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那个黑暗的时代并没有完全结束\Nthe dark ages never actually ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而且恐惧…\Nthat the fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,仇恨 还有凶残\Nhatred, and brutality
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这些曾经折磨过我们祖先的东西\Nthat once plagued our ancestors
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还在折磨着我们\Nplagues us still.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚\NTonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是我无上的荣耀\Nit is my sublime pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,来给你们展示一条光明大道\Nto demonstrate a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一条能走出这个黑暗的时代的光明大道\NOut of the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆生 爱迪生曾经认为它不过是个空想\NWhat Thomas Edison dismissed as mere fantasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:12:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,而尼古拉 特斯拉也没能成就它\Nwhat Nikola Tesla failed to bring to fruition,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我今晚却能展示给你们\NI give to you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,从磁层圈获取的能量\NPower drawn from the magnetosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这个无影无形的能量来源\Nthe same invisible source
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,正是指南针能指方向的原因\Nthat compels the needle on this compass to point North.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,经过我的科学家们\NHarnessed and amplified by my scientists
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,和技术员们处理和放大\Nand technicians,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我能给予你们免费的…\NI give to you free...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,安全的\Nsafe,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要线网的能源\Nwireless power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  第一步\NNow. Stage one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,大家听令！\NStand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,第一阶段！\NStage one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,开始！\NMark!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这事可能吗？\NIs such a thing possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,从理论上来说可以 我猜\NIn theory, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是若真的进入市场\NBut if it were brought to the market,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,会对石油能源是多大的冲击啊？\Nwhat effect would it have on our petroleum interests?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,粉碎性的 当然\NShattering, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么好担心的\NNothing we need worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,加大功率\NMore power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,加大功率\NMore power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,第二阶段！\NStage two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy\NLucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy  快看\NLucy, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,只是个把戏罢了\NSome sort of trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有根导线的\NThere must be a wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,—— 德古拉 ——
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 啊 快把它关了 现在！ - 啊啊！\N- Ah, shut that down, now! - Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正经历一些技术难题  先生\NExperiencing some technical difficulties, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只需再多几秒而已\NJust a few more seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来救救我们！\NSomebody help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我要着了！ 我要着了！\NI'm burning! I'm burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,冷却剂已经挥发了！\NThe coolant has evaporated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在关！\NI'm shutting down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 肯定只是个把戏  - 只是个把戏\N- It's a trick. - It's a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们 女士们\NLadies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们的耐心\NI thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信我们的小演示\NI trust our little demonstration was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很有启发意义\Nilluminating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy Westenra\NLucy Westenra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Westenra 小姐\NMiss Westenra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人陶醉\NRavishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Murray小姐  你看起来有点被吓到了\NMiss Murray, you look a little shaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定我刚目睹了什么\NI'm not sure what I've just witnessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,未来  Murray小姐\NThe future, Miss Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一个新时代的开始\NThe beginning of a new era.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker先生\NMister Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那么 明天  - 好的\N- Tomorrow, then. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 当然\NYes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那小子好像深深地迷上你了\NHe seems quite taken with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呦喂\NOoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那个名叫嫉妒的怪兽\NThe green-eyed monster
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在你心头作祟了哦\Nrears his ugly head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生不过是出于礼貌\NMister Grayson is just being polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢说 那并不只是社交礼节\NMore than polite, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧！我喝餐后酒去\NOoh! Cordials.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的事真是不同寻常啊\NThat was extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jayne小姐\NLady Jayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我都没感觉到你的到来\NI didn't hear you approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生 听您的语气\NYou say that as
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛这是我的一种了不起的能力\Nif it's an accomplishment, Mr. Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我Alexander吧\NAlexander, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander  你知道吗\NYou know, there's a touch of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,连经理都被你深深触动了\Nthe impresario about you, Alexander.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你今晚的展示\NYour performance this evening
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,简直如歌剧般激动人心\Nwas no less than operatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,介于我是歌剧的狂热票友\NAs I'm an ardent patron of the opera,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我就把这当做是对自己的恭维了\NI'll take that as a compliment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我很清楚  真实的情况\Nalthough I'm certain it was meant
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,与你的赞美截然不同\Nas quite the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 怎么会呢？\NOh, you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说你居然喜欢歌剧？\NSo you love the opera?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 我能成为第一个\NWell, may I be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,邀请你参加本轮歌剧献映季开幕的人吗？\Nto invite you to the opening of the season?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander 你就明说\NTell me, Alexander,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,愿不愿意和我同去啊？\Nwill you join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我已经订好自己的包厢了  - 好遗憾啊\N- I've reserved my own box. - Pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要是你在我的包厢\NI feel you'd enjoy the performance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会更加享受精彩的表演\Nso much more in mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会是那样的\NNo doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,诶\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,承蒙您的大驾光临不胜感激\NThank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以吻您的手吗？\NMay I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-Grayson先生- 您好\N- Mister Grayson. - Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你觉得就凭你今晚荒唐的把戏\NIf you think you fooled anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就能骗过哪个傻子的的话\Nwith that absurd stunt tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那你可是大错特错了\Nyou are sadly mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的如此不堪？\NAm I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是个骗子 小子\NYou are a fraud, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我保证\NAnd I will see to it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你绝不会再有机会在这里耍花招\Nthat you never do business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她是不会在原地一直等你的\NShe's not going to wait forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你若不及时求婚\NIf you don't ask her to marry you soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,别人就会取而代之\Nsomeone else is bound to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-哪个混球？-Grayson？\N- Who? - Grayson?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你可别傻了\NDon't be absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定没有注意到\NYou must've noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他是怎样深情的凝望着你\Nthe way he leered at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他可没有\NHe did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,至少他不像你家那位那么无趣\NAt least he's not boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我是那么喜欢和你呆在一起住\NAs much as I enjoy having you spend the night at my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们可不可以  就那么一次也好\Ncould we please, for once,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谈论下除了你和Jonathan呆在一起\Ntalk about something other than
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,多么无聊以外的事？\Nhow tedious you find Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一句  他并不无聊\NAnd besides, he's not boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说的是\NWhat I'm saying is that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她能找到一个更好的人选\Nshe could do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到什么了吗？\NDo you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啊。\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你说那是什么？\NWhat do you suppose it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-晚安 Clive先生 -晚安\N- Good night, Mr. Clive. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,马车 开走吧\NHorse, move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,此人就是一猪猡\NThe man was a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他在我的地界撒野\NHe insulted me under my own roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你就把他撕成碎片了？\NSo you tear the man to pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们要贴个警告牌\NPerhaps we should mount a warning sign
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在前门上\Nover the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就告诉你\NI told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的贪污腐败骄纵自大\Ntheir corruption
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,已经到了无法无天的地步\Nand their hubris is unbridled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,恶龙会一贯如此\NThat's always been the way with the Order of the Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们仍能觉察它的痕迹\NStill, it's one thing to hear it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,用我们的眼睛就能察觉到\Nquite another to see it with one's own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,从那对头衔\NReadily identified by
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,急切到荒谬的执念\Ntheir overtly grotesque
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就能清楚的发现是恶龙会的人\Nsense of entitlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这个家伙 Laurent大人\NLike this one, Lord Laurent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,洋洋得意的孔雀男\NPreening little peacock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这个  大人  他叫什么名字？\NAnd the other one, Lord what's-his-name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Davenport. - Davenport.\N- Davenport. - Davenport.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,上院里的两个渣滓\NThese two stink of high council.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们的名字写在名单上\NPut them on the short list.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,您认为谁是他们的头子？\NWho do you suppose is the leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是这名单里的任何一个\NCould be any one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也可能哪个都不是\NOr none.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,多么的乏味啊\NHow very innocuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可您已点燃他们的怒火 Renfiled\NBut you cross them, Renfield,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他们对您将如同\Nand they will strike you down
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,困在井中的蝮蛇一般凶残\Nlike vipers in a pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:20:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谋杀 拷打 奸淫 灭门\NMurder, torture, rape, wholesale slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这可都是恶龙会的惯用手法\NThat is the stock-in-trade of the Order of the Dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,说实在的用了五百年了\Nand has been for over 500 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在我年轻之时\NIn my past,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们更加露骨的达成目的\Nthey asserted their will more directly
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,用那弓与剑\Nvia the cross and the sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,整村一个不留\Nslaughtering entire villages,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,给男男女女贴上异教徒的标签\Nbranding men and women heretics.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,活活把他们烧死\NBurning them alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睁睁的看着他们尖叫着被火焰吞噬\Nand watching them burn, screaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,只是为了无人见过的主神\NFor a God who never came.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们在私人俱乐部和会议室的掩护下\NNow they do their dirty work
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,继续做着肮脏的勾当\Nvia private clubs and boardrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他们控制商业 贿赂政客 控制石油\NThey employ business, politics, and oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而最后的那个 Renfield\NAnd that last thing, Renfield,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,将会是他们的命门\Nwill be their undoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们相信\NThey believe
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,下个世纪将会在石油的滋养下蔓生\Nit will fuel the next century.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他们可以控制石油\NAnd if they control it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,未来就是他们的\Nthey control the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但从我们证实了\NBut from the moment we demonstrate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,生物能源的可行性的那一刻起\Nthe viability of geomagnetic technology...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,呼！\NPoof!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,金钱就不会流进腰包\NNo more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,权力也会离他们而去\NNo more power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而恶龙会也将土崩瓦解\NNo more Order of the Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经充分检查过了？\NHe performed a full examination?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.20,0:23:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,流程一点不差\NAs instructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.37,0:23:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,从何看出是吸血鬼掠食的结果？\NAny signs of vampiric feeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.30,0:23:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,颈部损伤太大\NToo much damage to the neck
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.11,0:23:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,无法判断\Nto make a positive determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他砍下了这个人的脑袋\NSo he severs the man's head
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.31,0:23:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,把他装扮成法国烤母鸡\Nand dresses him up like a roasted French hen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.41,0:23:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不得不这么做\NWell, it had to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.46,0:23:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的\NYou know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,从何时起吸血鬼开始\NHow long has it been since a vampire stalked
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.82,0:24:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在街头横行？ 七年前？\Nthe streets of this city? Seven years?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.69,0:24:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,八年了\NEight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.29,0:24:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  对  白教堂血案\NYes, the Whitechapel killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.36,0:24:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  看看我们惹上的麻烦事\NGod, when I think of the trouble we went to,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.53,0:24:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,毁尸灭迹\Nmutilating the victims to hide the signs,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.70,0:24:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那些我们写给报社的荒谬信件\Nthose absurd letters we wrote to the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.17,0:24:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  开膛手杰克\NHuh. Jack the Ripper, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.40,0:24:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说什么?\NWhat do you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.21,0:24:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,除非有其他的证明\NWell, unless proven otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.81,0:24:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我们必须假定Clive\NI think we must assume that Clive
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.45,0:24:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,被我们的敌人袭击了\Nwas targeted by our enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.31,0:24:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不论看上去是否自然\Nwhether natural or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.52,0:24:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我会安排Kruger巡逻\NI will put Kruger on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.12,0:24:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,让他盯紧理事\NHave him keep an eye on the high council members' houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.15,0:24:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一直?  - 不是\N- Indefinitely? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.16,0:24:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,直到时间与事实可以证明\NJust until time or events
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.54,0:24:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不过是孤独谨慎\Nproves us overcautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.53,0:24:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他在这儿你都不一定知道呢\NYou won't even know he's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.73,0:24:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,记住别走漏风声\NSee to it that we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.16,0:24:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们两个人的秘密\NThis is strictly between you and me for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.93,0:24:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大家已经够紧张兮兮的了\NWe don't want to make the others any more nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.73,0:24:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们不能让他们徒增烦恼  - 嗯\N- than they already are. - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.67,0:24:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人问起\NAnd if anyone asks
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.77,0:24:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就说他是被狗咬死的\NHe was killed by a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.24,0:24:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你上道了\NGood girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.51,0:24:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了血淋淋的东西\NAnd take that bloody thing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.35,0:25:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,神经元组织\NThe structure of the neuron is absolutely distinct
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.65,0:25:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,同身体其他部位的细胞不一样\Nfrom all other cells in the human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.92,0:25:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Campbell先生?\NMister Campbell?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.93,0:25:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我们…\NSorry, sir. We weren't, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.26,0:25:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Van Helsing教授?\NProfessor Van Helsing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.90,0:25:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  Murray女士?\NYes, Miss Murray?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.30,0:25:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Campbell先生只是在向他的同事指出\NMister Campbell was only pointing out to his colleagues
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.33,0:25:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,新闻头版提到的电脉冲是如何产生的\Nhow analogous certain aspects of the front-page article regarding
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.07,0:25:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,与您今天的讲课主题\Nthe generation of electrical impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.81,0:25:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是如何相似\Nare to the subject of your lecture today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.44,0:25:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Campbell先生?\NMister Campbell?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.49,0:25:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Campbell先生  相当正确\NQuite right, Mister Campbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.05,0:25:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生的新技术\NMister Grayson's new
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.36,0:25:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,和我今天要讲的主题有密切关系\Ntechnology is germane to the subject at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.32,0:25:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  我建议你\NHowever, I would suggest
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.56,0:25:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在课外讨论这一观察成果\Nthat you discuss such observations outside of class.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.71,0:26:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生呆会儿会来\NMister Grayson will be right with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.56,0:26:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker先生\NMister Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.06,0:26:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,您能来真是太好了\NHow good of you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.01,0:26:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐\NPlease, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.84,0:26:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,来点酒吗?\NWould you like some wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.14,0:26:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好像早了点  谢谢\NIt's a, um, bit early for me, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.85,0:26:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢威士忌\NI prefer whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.75,0:27:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,您应该知道我的编辑\NYou should know my editor
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.17,0:27:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,认为您多少有吹牛的成分\Nbelieves you're after some sort of puffery.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.66,0:27:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 吹牛?  - 是的\N- Puffery? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.46,0:27:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么会这么想呢?\NAnd why would he think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.27,0:27:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有采访过几次\NI don't field many interview
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.72,0:27:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,像您这样有地位的人\Nrequests from those in your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.67,0:27:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说富豪?\NYou mean the wealthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.30,0:27:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我是说权贵\NNo, I mean the privileged.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.97,0:27:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,通常他们都会回避\NUsually, they run the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.21,0:27:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为\NThat's because
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.53,0:27:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你一旦和我有一样的既得利益\Nyou stand against the same
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.61,0:27:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就会希望我回美国\Nvested interests that would prefer I return to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.14,0:27:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我想没人注意到\NI didn't think anyone had noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.88,0:27:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我注意到了\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.18,0:27:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是我请你来采访的原因\NThat's precisely why I invited you for this interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.79,0:27:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可以开始了吗?\NShall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.72,0:27:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NVery well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.62,0:27:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是英国?\NWhy England?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.99,0:27:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我曾祖父母的家乡\NThis is the country of my great-grandparents' birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.16,0:27:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是归国\NIn that regard, it's a homecoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.76,0:27:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,和Edison将你赶出美国\NAnd it has nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.11,0:27:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没有一点关系?\Nwith Edison running you out of the States?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.50,0:27:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.77,0:27:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,欧洲人的说话方式别具一格\NEurope speaks to me in a way no other place does.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.51,0:27:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是我们称之为"旧世界"的原因\NYou know, we call it "The Old World" For a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.11,0:28:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们无论在哪都追求新事物\NAnd yet, her people seek the new wherever they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.28,0:28:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白这种挣扎\NI understand this struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.41,0:28:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我是古老家族的后代\NI, myself, am descended from a very old family.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.95,0:28:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的心里永远向往未来\NBut my mind, always fixed on the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.92,0:28:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我会用两种思维方式来思考\NI surround myself with things that speak to both.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.99,0:28:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你很矛盾  对吧?\NYou're full of contradictions, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.59,0:28:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,世界原本就是矛盾的\NSo is the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.13,0:28:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是我想和你交流的原因\NThat is precisely why I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.30,0:28:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在大变革的关口上\NYou see, we're on the precipice of a great change.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.10,0:28:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开始重新定义\NWe have it within ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.24,0:28:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的物种\Nto redefine our species.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.24,0:28:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…  你说“物种”\NWait, you...You say "Species"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.45,0:28:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好像人是动物似的\NAs though people are animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.84,0:28:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么意思?\NWhat do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.94,0:28:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不是达尔文先生教我们的吗?\NIs that not what Mister Darwin taught us?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.45,0:28:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,进化论?\NThat man evolves?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.15,0:28:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这一理论就是我努力的原因\NThat is what I've come here to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.08,0:28:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,促进人类的演变\NTo facilitate in that evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.89,0:28:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说  帮助自然进化\NGive nature a helping hand, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.77,0:29:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Murray女士  - 教授\N- Miss Murray. - Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.51,0:29:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧  请坐\NCome in. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.18,0:29:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么事?\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.25,0:29:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,额  恩  我们\NWell, um, we will soon be
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.55,0:29:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就快期末考了\Nundergoing our final examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.49,0:29:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 你也知道\N- Yes. - And as you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.86,0:29:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,得分最高的学生\Nthe student who scores the highest will be given
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.09,0:29:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有机会成为你的研究助理\Nthe opportunity to serve as your research assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.96,0:29:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.43,0:29:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你的分数一直是班上最高的\NYou have consistently scored the highest marks in class
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.73,0:29:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不论是笔试还是口试\Nfor every written and oral exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.83,0:29:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可是…  我的外科技术…\N- However... My surgical technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.60,0:29:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,仍然有待提高  没错\N...leaves much to be desired, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.71,0:29:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,教授  您简直无法想象我练习了多少次\NProfessor, I can't tell you how often I practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.81,0:29:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是每当手术刀要割破皮肤表皮的那一刻\Nbut the moment the scalpel pierces the epidermis,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.31,0:29:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我就…\Nwell...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.95,0:29:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不论我怎么做\Nmy hands begin to tremble
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.87,0:29:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手都抖个不停  他们…\Nand no matter what I do, they...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.42,0:29:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina…\NMina...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.98,0:29:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现\NI have always found that
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.29,0:29:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,保持手不抖的秘诀\Nthe secret to a steady hand
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.81,0:29:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就是保持一颗平静的心\Nis a steady heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.76,0:29:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不明白  - 你必须相信自己\N- I don't understand. - You must believe in yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.43,0:30:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,相信以你的能力能够治愈别人\Nin your abilities to heal others.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.76,0:30:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这么简单\NIt is that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.30,0:30:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我信自己\NBut I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.73,0:30:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此  你会成功的\NIf so, then you will succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.50,0:30:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,到那时  你会明白…\NUntil then, know this...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.04,0:30:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,心是不会说谎的\NThe heart never lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.01,0:30:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.15,0:30:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对  好的  我同意\NYes, well, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.01,0:30:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 晚安  - 晚安\N- Well, good night. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.15,0:30:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.79,0:31:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.53,0:31:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你等了这么久\NSorry to have kept you waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.65,0:31:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.59,0:31:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生真是慷慨\NIt was very generous of
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.95,0:31:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,让你用他的包厢\NMister Grayson to give you his box tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.53,0:31:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是想让我写点\NWell, he obviously wants me
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.77,0:31:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,夸赞他的东西  不是吗？\Nto write nice things about him, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.97,0:31:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.50,0:31:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,像Grayson先生这样的人\NA man such as Grayson is so desperate
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.77,0:32:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然迫不及待地巴结你\Nto court favor with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.57,0:32:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定对他那金碧辉煌的房子\NYou'd think he'd be satisfied with his beautiful home
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.04,0:32:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那些优美的画作\Nand all those brilliant paintings
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.74,0:32:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,和高科技非常满意\Nand the thrilling technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.28,0:32:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,更不要提他那漂亮的脸蛋\Nnot to mention his good looks
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.33,0:32:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,和非凡的魅力\Nand charisma.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.48,0:32:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.15,0:32:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,的确令人印象深刻\NYes, it's very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.75,0:32:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你有他永远也没有的东西\NBut then you have something that he will never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.66,0:32:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.52,0:32:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我\NMe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.36,0:33:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,从这后面看视角更好点\NThe view is much better from back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.86,0:33:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?  我从来不知道\NIs it? I can't imagine that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.40,0:33:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一起看怎么样？\NWhy don't you join me and see?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.32,0:34:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对 没错 的确是惊人\NWhy, yes, it is. It is astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.30,0:34:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你是被冷落了\NI trust you were unobserved?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.86,0:34:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你也确实要求我“谨慎”的陪伴\NYour invitation did request my "Discreet company".
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.17,0:34:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  虽然我还担心\NYes, it did. Though I was concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.10,0:34:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你作为一个美国人可能会\Nas an American, that you might not understand
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.90,0:34:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不理解“谨慎”的意思\Nthe meaning of the word "Discreet."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.17,0:34:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我的确需要查字典看看\NI had to look it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.44,0:34:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我  还有什么词语\NTell me, what other words
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.89,0:34:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是你需要查询的\Ndid you have to look up?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.92,0:34:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,贪婪无比\NInsatiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.73,0:34:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,无可救药\NIncorrigible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.65,0:35:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,难以抑制\NUnquenchable.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.86,0:35:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Clive先生下葬不到一天\NSir Clive not a day in the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.16,0:35:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson就像禽兽一样\Nand Grayson descends on his widow
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.72,0:35:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,打劫了他的妻子\Nlike a bird of prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.56,0:35:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,带走了Clive的整箱冷却剂\NLocked up Clive's entire block of imperial coolant.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.60,0:35:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她为什么要卖给他？\NWhy on earth would she sell out to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.40,0:35:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他为Clive还清了赌债\NHe purchased the paper on Clive's gambling debts,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.64,0:35:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,并要挟要起诉他的房产权\Nand threatened to sue his estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.01,0:35:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 天啊!  - 所以她没有选择\N- Good God! - So you see, she had no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.81,0:35:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,只有接受交易以防丑闻外传\Nbut to trade the stock in order to avert a scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.88,0:35:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这整档子事真恶心\NAbsolutely loathsome, the whole damned business.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.01,0:35:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但你必须承认  很精彩\NBut you must admit, well played.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.62,0:35:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得轻松\NThat's easy for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.68,0:35:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他又不是你的商业伙伴\NHe's not your business partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.39,0:35:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不一定\NOh, he's hardly that, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.55,0:35:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只是董事会的一个席位而已\NIt's just a seat on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.09,0:35:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是控有股权\NNot as if he has a controlling interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.11,0:36:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kruger\NKruger.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.55,0:36:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.46,0:36:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.47,0:36:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.61,0:36:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,地狱之火!\NBurn in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.52,0:37:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,“死去的猎人兄弟\N"Thou died fair and well,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.83,0:37:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,安息吧”\Nbrother huntsman killed."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.72,0:37:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,“在你静寂前\N"Impaled the hearts of many beasts,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.43,0:37:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,已刺穿无数野兽的胸膛”\Nbefore thine own was stilled."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.23,0:37:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,死之前\NBefore you die,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.97,0:37:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,鼓起勇气\Ntake heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.70,0:37:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就到地狱了…\NYou will soon be joined in hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.37,0:37:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,同你的兄弟们一样\Nby scores of your brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.51,0:37:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我会摧毁你们的秩序…\NI will destroy your Order...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.84,0:37:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,以及一切秩序代表\Nand everything it stands for.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.55,0:37:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…\NYou are...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.05,0:37:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dracula\NDracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.44,0:38:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.42,0:38:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管练吧  但无法挽救你\NPractice all you want. It won't save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.75,0:38:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,说话了\NIt speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.95,0:38:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,挽救我什么？\NSave me from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.76,0:38:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,把你带到伦敦的人？\NThe one that drew you to London?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.66,0:38:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没人带我来\NNo one drew me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.69,0:38:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.79,0:38:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你一无是处\NYou're nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.63,0:38:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是被腐烂的臭味吸引的苍蝇\NAn errant fly attracted by the stench of rot.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.43,0:38:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你主人的名字！\NTell me your sire's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.64,0:38:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你的物种是有宿命的\NYou know, there's fates for your kind
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.84,0:38:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,比死更糟  我清楚得很\Na lot worse than death, and I know them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.48,0:38:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为在湖底腐蚀要话\NHow long do you think
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.15,0:38:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,需要多久的时间\Nit's going to take for this to rust
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.01,0:38:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,几年？  几十年？\Nat the bottom of a lake? Years? Decades?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.92,0:38:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,随便你怎么样\NDo what you will to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.48,0:38:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,会有人紧跟其后\NThere will be another who follows,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.02,0:38:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不久之后  一个又一个 很快的\Nand another, and another, and soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.96,0:38:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不久之后？\NSoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.59,0:39:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会成为一个军团\NWe will be legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.82,0:39:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才在想你会什么时候进来\NI was wondering when you'd make your entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.69,0:39:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,计划本来是让Clive大人的债务\NThe plan was to leverage
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.83,0:39:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,杠杆扩大\NSir Clive's gambling debts
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.40,0:39:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,违背他的利益\Nagainst his interests,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.03,0:39:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不是他的遗孀的利益\Nnot his widow's.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.90,0:39:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了一个机会\NI saw an opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.27,0:39:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,并抓住了这个机会\Nand I seized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.50,0:39:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你的行为冲动又鲁莽\NIt was impetuous and careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.81,0:39:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但任务完成了\NIt got the job done.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.98,0:39:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,需要我解释多少次\NHow many times must I explain the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.18,0:39:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,家族世仇和报复的不同？\Nbetween a vendetta and vengeance?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.38,0:39:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这不能演变为一场消耗战\NThis cannot become a war of attrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.75,0:40:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就像一条九头蛇\NThe Order Draco is like the Hydra.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.32,0:40:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,切下一个蛇头  它会长出两个取而代之\NCut off a head, they grow two to replace it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.09,0:40:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣\NFunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.86,0:40:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,发生在Clive大人身上的不是这样的\NThat's not what happened to Sir Clive's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.52,0:40:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,别傻了\NDon't be a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.83,0:40:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道摧毁他们惟一的方法\NYou know the only way to crush them
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.25,0:40:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就是消灭他们\Nis to wipe out
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.49,0:40:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们力量的特有来源　\Nthe very source of their power,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.05,0:40:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们巨大的财富\Ntheir vast wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.16,0:40:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,十多年了　　\NFor over a decade
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.96,0:40:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们设计并建造了这座谎言帝国\Nwe've schemed and built this empire of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.17,0:40:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会允许因为你的缺乏纪律\NI will not have our work undone
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.89,0:40:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们的事业无法完成\Nby your lack of discipline!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.01,0:40:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.11,0:40:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.45,0:40:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,给我一个不把你的皮\NGive me one good reason
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.08,0:40:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,像葡萄一样剥掉的好理由\NI should not peel you like a grape.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.92,0:40:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要是没有我\NBecause without me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.89,0:40:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在那个铁盒子里烂着呢\Nyou'd still be rotting in that iron box.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.97,0:41:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我会被激怒吗？\NDo you think I am not immune to rage?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.02,0:41:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,恶龙会屠杀了全部家人！\NThe Order of the Dragon slaughtered my entire family!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.92,0:41:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能放弃自己的本能\NWe must not give in to our base instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.19,0:41:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须练习控制力\NWe must practice control.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.33,0:41:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们必须按照计划行事  - 确实\N- We must follow the plan! - True.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.33,0:41:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的憎恨\NOur hatred
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.45,0:41:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,始于同一个严酷的考验\Nwas born in the same crucible.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.73,0:41:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你赋予了它行事\NYou give it form.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.77,0:41:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但我赋予了它力量！\NBut I give it strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.67,0:41:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是因为所失去的\NWe are not bound by
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.51,0:41:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,而结合在一起\Nwhat we have lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.64,0:41:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而是因为夺走的人\Nbut by who took it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.78,0:41:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.61,0:41:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们杀死了我的妻子！\NThey killed my wife!
